{"tid":813013,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"山竹颱風打到黎！香港人必睇【狂暴天災：超強颱風】","createTime":"2018-09-10T06:06:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T01:49:25.000Z","uid":173631,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"25a2af25e9e7a96a07b1c98ab5fe0f854d4d1b67","tid":813013,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T06:06:12.000Z","msg":"歷史再重演<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/10/140422_678cbfbfc74c4225e3259a1dad3ccca7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F10%2F140422_678cbfbfc74c4225e3259a1dad3ccca7.jpg&h=2ba52541&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/10/140604_678cbfbfc74c4225e3259a1dad3ccca7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F10%2F140604_678cbfbfc74c4225e3259a1dad3ccca7.jpg&h=2162ae2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.timedg.com/sjb/p/20703574.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.timedg.com%2Fsjb%2Fp%2F20703574.html&d=aYDE9KzYsOpxgFxiHX9xq54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=5df0e355\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.timedg.com/sjb/p/20703574.html</a>台風&ldquo;山竹&rdquo;已生成！最強可達17級以上，可能嚴重影響東莞丨ⅰ看新聞<br />\n台風&ldquo;山竹&rdquo;已生成！最強可達 17 級以上<br />\n<br />\n東莞時間網訊 今年第22號台風&quot;山竹&quot;9日上午由強熱帶風暴級加強為台風級，10日5時其中心位於距東莞3780公裏的西北太平洋洋面上中心附近，最大風力13級（38米/秒）。預計&quot;山竹&quot;將以30公裏時速向偏西方向移動，強度繼續加強，趨向菲律賓呂宋島東北部一帶沿海，15日靠近巴士海峽，最強可達超強台風級（17級或17級以上，60-65米/秒）。<br />\n<br />\n本周將有兩個台風影響我省<br />\n<br />\n巴士海峽附近的熱帶擾動已於10日08時加強為熱帶低壓（6級），其中心位於我市東偏南方向約850公裏的巴士海峽海面上。預計，熱帶低壓24小時內將以10公裏左右的時速向偏西方向移動，11日移入南海後移速加快，並將加強為今年第23號台風，於13日白天在廣東電白到海南瓊海之間的沿海地區登陸。受其影響，12日到13日我市沿海地區有6級左右陣風，雷陣雨頻繁，累計雨量有中到大雨。<br />\n<br />\n台風&ldquo;山竹&rdquo;可能嚴重影響東莞<br />\n<br />\n另外，今年第22號台風&ldquo;山竹&rdquo;15日前後移入南海海面，16日到17日將可能嚴重影響我市。請關註並做好各項防禦準備工作。（東莞市氣象台9月10日11時50分發布）<br />\n<br />\n東莞未來十天天氣預報<br />\n<br />\n預計我市10-11日多雲，局部有陣雨；12日南海低壓靠近，有陣雨或雷陣雨；13日受熱帶低壓東北側東南氣流影響，雷陣雨頻繁，累計雨量有中到大雨；14-15日受&ldquo;山竹&rdquo;外圍下沈氣流影響，高溫炎熱；16-17日將可能受&ldquo;山竹&rdquo;嚴重影響，有狂風暴雨天氣過程；展望18-19日多雲，有陣雨或雷陣雨。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/to6zME66tVU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fto6zME66tVU&d=aYDE9KzYsOpxgFxiHX9xq54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=810af784\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/to6zME66tVU</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GVPpkqy0AiA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGVPpkqy0AiA&d=aYDE9KzYsOpxgFxiHX9xq54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=50c3cc03\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GVPpkqy0AiA</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-So1sk358qI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-So1sk358qI&d=aYDE9KzYsOpxgFxiHX9xq54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=07a5ab38\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-So1sk358qI</a>"},{"pid":"592c873265406c92e9f81291d41230ce0c4c0597","tid":813013,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T07:17:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4def968c46a0ae1e87be8085f93c04265e67cc2","tid":813013,"uid":61277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T19:54:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b49ef842ec86aa5229639f0e41c6d538999a1447","tid":813013,"uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T20:26:54.000Z","msg":"樓主個版本好低清<br />\n<br />\nyoutube有720p"},{"pid":"10d7273151b0f2565161eb0b25471525638169ff","tid":813013,"uid":34522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b49ef842ec86aa5229639f0e41c6d538999a1447","tid":813013,"uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T20:26:54.000Z","msg":"樓